> I'd rather feel like a fool than feel that it's easy for *anybody* to
> decrypt anything I say.  If you're too busy flaming D.S. to respond to
> this, then I guess he's achieved his goal.

You're hardly an idiot for suggesting session keys be negotiated using
ROT13, but it could be said that session keys are pretty basic stuff
and of course, it's in the FAQ.  But no problem...

